org.revapi.java.spi

Interface TypeEnvironment


  • public interface TypeEnvironment
    This interface mimics (to an extent) the ProcessingEnvironment and serves the same purpose. To give a context to the API checking classes.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Lukas Krejci

      • visitUseSites

        @Nullable
<R,P> R visitUseSites(@Nonnull
                                TypeElement type,
                                @Nonnull
                                UseSite.Visitor<R,P> visitor,
                                @Nullable
                                P parameter)
        Visits the uses of the provided type. The visit will stop as soon as a non-null value is returned from the visitor, even if some use sites are left unvisited.
        Type Parameters:
        R - the return type (use Void for no return type)
        P - the type of the parameter (use Void for no particular type)
        Parameters:
        type - the type to visit uses of
        visitor - the visitor
        parameter - the parameter to supply to the visitor
        Returns:
        the value returned by the visitor
